---
description: Detect and prevent insecure design patterns in JavaScript applications as defined in OWASP Top 10:2021-A04
globs: **/*.js, **/*.jsx, **/*.ts, **/*.tsx, !**/node_modules/**, !**/dist/**, !**/build/**, !**/coverage/**
